OL,3,CLandlords required to licence Jersey
OL,4,Crental homes under landmark law
OL,6,FIt will soon be illegal to rent out a
OL,7,Fhome in without a licence.
OL,9,FA landmark new scheme requiring all
OL,10,Flandlords to apply for the permit will
OL,11,Fopen online on Wednesday 1 May as part
OL,12,Fof work to improve the overall
OL,13,Fstandards of rental accommodation on
OL,14,Fthe island.
OL,16,FA licence will cost #60 per home and
OL,17,Flast for two years.
