OL,4,Crental homes under landmark law
OL,6,FThere will be a three-month grace
OL,7,Fperiod when properties do not need to
OL,8,Fbe inspected to be issued with a
OL,9,Fpermit.
OL,11,FIt will become mandatory from Thursday
OL,12,F1 August, after which checks may be
OL,13,Fneeded before a licence is issued.
OL,15,FThe change was first proposed by
OL,16,FJersey's former Environment Minister,
OL,17,FDeputy Jonathan Renouf, and approved
OL,18,Fby States' members in November 2023.
