OL,6,FIt is hoped the scheme will give
OL,7,Fofficials better information about
OL,8,Fwhich properties are being rented and
OL,9,Fwho to work with when improvements are
OL,10,Fneeded.
OL,12,FEnvironment Minister, Deputy Steve
OL,13,FLuce, explained: "The online licence
OL,14,Fapplication process is being
OL,15,Fstreamlined to be as straightforward
OL,16,Fas possible, and I don't see it as
OL,17,Fbeing a massive burden for landlords
OL,18,Fto complete.
