OL,3,CLandlords required to licence Jersey
OL,4,Crental homes under landmark law
OL,6,F"This is about the health and safety
OL,7,Fof tenants and ensuring the homes
OL,8,Fislanders live in meet certain
OL,9,Fstandards.
OL,11,F"We know there are many good landlords
OL,12,Fin Jersey, but there are also too many
OL,13,Ftenants having to live in mouldy
OL,14,Fproperties, or perhaps homes where the
OL,15,Ffire alarm doesn't work, or where the
OL,16,Fstaircases simply aren't safe to
OL,17,Fclimb."
OL,19,FA series of information events are
OL,20,Fbeing held in parish halls between
OL,21,FTuesday 23 and Thursday 25 April 2024.
